  Devops Application :
  Build Process (Stages.)
  ======
  Repository : Code (SCM ) : Source code management (.txt why not?) >> Histroy (GIT) 
  clone >> update >> add >> push >> central location. >> stable/master.
  Project : jave : compile >> code Review >> Build >> Test(unit case) >> build >> [jar, war ,ear ] >> 

  build [jar, war,ear] >> Push Artifactory >> Deployment (jenkins) {Fetch artifact from artifactory >> env file >> deploy}
  build [Images ] >> artifactory pushing >> Deployment >> Host Platform >> Orchestartion tools [Docker Swarm, Kubernetes, AWS Beanstalk, EKS, AKS, Rancher ]
  Rancher : Orc management >> backend Kuberenets >> cattle orc engine >> SSL >> RBAC (docker-compose -- rancher-compose)
  DockerFile and Docker-Compose


  PC/Browser[www.google.com] >> ISP >> Internal DNS Servers >>  Root DNS Server >> TLD(Top Level Domain) >> .com >> Google Servers

  Load Balancer(DMZ). 80/443 [haproxy/nginx/httpd] >> Mulesoft External gateway >> Frontend API Gateway >> Frontend Service >> Gmail Service >>
  www.gogole.com/AUTH

  service registry >> USER/Statement/Document/servicing/sso/AUTH

  >> WebServer >> Application Server >> Database 

